{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b1d8ed3b61","title":"关于了解河北省博野县农业合作社整顿情况的两个批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"76ee45ffec","index":0,"year":1955,"month":9,"day":13,"articleId":"b1d8ed3b61"},{"id":"ed14594d8c","index":1,"year":1955,"month":10,"day":23,"articleId":"b1d8ed3b61"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"bc3581347b","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林铁，当时任中共河北省委书记、河北省省长。"},{"id":"983710dd9a","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"叶子龙，当时任毛泽东的秘书。"},{"id":"3c221253e0","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指林铁1955年10月20日关于检查博野县工作情况给毛泽东的信。信中说，在接到毛泽东批转的钟顺通写的情况汇报后，河北省委即派出工作组协同当地干部在博野县三个乡进行了检查，实际情况是：在今年4月间，省农林厅训练班学员100多人曾到该县实习，并进行过一次十种表格登记，确实未解决多少问题。通过这次检查，存在的问题已引起博野县委注意，除检查时已解决一部分外，县委正结合今年建社，在继续进行整顿中加以解决。"}],"contents":[{"id":"13d2e86a0e","type":"title","text":"关于了解河北省博野县农业合作社整顿情况的两个批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61"},{"id":"bc3581347b","type":"paragraph","text":"此件送河北省委林铁同志阅。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61"},{"id":"983710dd9a","type":"paragraph","text":"钟顺通是我们这里的一个警卫工作人员。据他说，博野县有些合作社并没有认真去整顿。请省委注意此事，如果属实，应设法加以解决。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61"},{"id":"3c221253e0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61"},{"id":"5411a03191","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61"},{"id":"831943112b","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]指钟顺通1955年8月5日写的他的家乡河北省博野县徐家营、杜各庄、北延三个乡的农业合作社的情况汇报。汇报中谈到整社情况时说，这次整社只把财产、社名、社长、社的主要干部进行了登记，而社里存在的问题没有进行解决。农民要求，秋后一定要整顿农业合作社，整顿干部和党员，加强对农村干部特别是乡、村、社干部的政策思想教育。叶子龙电话告林铁同志：","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61"},{"id":"a9deb72d3a","type":"paragraph","text":"此信收到了，谢谢他","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61"},{"id":"250b849ff5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61"},{"id":"720038cb55","type":"paragraph","text":"十月廿三日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61"}],"page":{"id":"1a5ebe0c77","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"b1d8ed3b61","start":365,"end":366}}}},"__N_SSG":true}